#

Warm Vegetable Salad with Herbed Dressing

$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Tags:

VeganHealthy

Description

A colorful medley of roasted seasonal vegetables served warm, drizzled with a vibrant herbed dressing for a delightful flavor boost.

Ingredients

  • Zucchini: 1 medium, sliced
  • Bell Peppers: 2, diced (red and yellow)
  • Carrots: 2, peeled and sliced
  • Asparagus: 1 cup, trimmed
  • Red Onion: 1 medium, sliced
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Fresh Parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
